amic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/151085/', '', 'Norethisterone, Nafarelin, Octreotide, Cetrorelix, Estradiol, Ganirelix, Relugolix, Lanreotide, Gonadorelin', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Ropeginterferon alfa-2b, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, More', 1767369485);
